  "2159650": {
    "name": "Drift: Space Survival",
    "steam_appid": 2159650,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "Drift: Space Survival是一个设置在神秘小行星带中的合作生存冒险。单独或与朋友一起制造、建造和探索，以重建你在研究船坠毁时失去的技术。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >共同冒险</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159650/extras/c1164300a1250c2a8ade825235626129.poster.avif?t=1729000462\" width=600 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159650/extras/c1164300a1250c2a8ade825235626129.webm?t=1729000462\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159650/extras/c1164300a1250c2a8ade825235626129.mp4?t=1729000462\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>与最多7名朋友一起，控制小行星，建造宏伟的飞船，并一起深入小行星带。留意奇特的生物。在这片遥远的太空中，你永远不知道会发现什么。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >打造你的星际飞船</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159650/extras/c13f3ebeb9462925780cf28c5dbb990b.poster.avif?t=1729000462\" width=600 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159650/extras/c13f3ebeb9462925780cf28c5dbb990b.webm?t=1729000462\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159650/extras/c13f3ebeb9462925780cf28c5dbb990b.mp4?t=1729000462\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你的研究船，曾经是一个充满科学活动的小镇，现在几乎完全消失了。利用你收集的资源重新建造它。生命支持和其他先进系统可以减轻太空生活的压力。从小行星带上带回的物资会让它感觉像家。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索这片区域</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159650/extras/26014d4199b4f9e981f3f0f2466533bd.poster.avif?t=1729000462\" width=600 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159650/extras/26014d4199b4f9e981f3f0f2466533bd.webm?t=1729000462\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159650/extras/26014d4199b4f9e981f3f0f2466533bd.mp4?t=1729000462\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这片区域不仅仅有大石头。带上你的朋友，一块石头接一块石头地探索宇宙，寻找你需要的资源和答案。Curtis Schweitzer的美妙音轨将伴随你进行探险。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >制作和自动化</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159650/extras/4b7dc05f0952aa615f4d8ca35de8f6bb.poster.avif?t=1729000462\" width=600 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159650/extras/4b7dc05f0952aa615f4d8ca35de8f6bb.webm?t=1729000462\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159650/extras/4b7dc05f0952aa615f4d8ca35de8f6bb.mp4?t=1729000462\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这超出了你能手工处理的范围。制作生存装备、多功能工具升级、牵引光束等来帮助你在旅途中生存。拥抱自动化的力量，让机器为你工作，而你深入未知。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >重新发现太空技术</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159650/extras/50e9840d96a7d545e11359acbf381f95.poster.avif?t=1729000462\" width=600 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159650/extras/50e9840d96a7d545e11359acbf381f95.webm?t=1729000462\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159650/extras/50e9840d96a7d545e11359acbf381f95.mp4?t=1729000462\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你很幸运还活着，但你并不孤单。一个基本的维护无人机设法留在船上，并准备学习。一起收集和研究你需要的技术，以制造回家的技术。",
